disclose the amount. Ian Campbell, general director of the opera, said he 
learned of Soviero's withdrawal by reading a Paris Opera brochure. He said that 
the singer had asked last May to be released from her contract for the Paris 
engagement, but had been denied because he felt that he owed his audience the 
promised performance.BETH KLEID 
