<TEXT>
<P>
The International Amateur Athletics Federation called on South African and 
African representatives to consider returning South Africa to international 
track and field competition. 
</P>
<P>
The appeal came a week after Juan Antonio Samaranch, president of the 
International Olympic Committee, said that the IOC would await a recommendation 
from African nations on whether South Africa would be readmitted to the Olympic 
Games. 
</P>
