LIBERIA -- REVOLTS; SHOOTINGS -- LIBERIA; DOE, SAMUEL K; PRISONERS -- LIBERIA; 
MILITARY CONFRONTATIONS; JOHNSON, PRINCE; TAYLOR, CHARLES MCARTHUR; UNITED 
STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- LIBERIA 
</P>
