sale and possible demolition. THOMAS KELSEY / Los Angeles Times; Photo, The 
Wichstand coffee shop was a tribute to the Googie architecture style, which was 
designed to catch the eye of passing motorists. Jack Laxer Photography 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
