Marnie Mosiman and Jarion Monroe. ; Photo, John de Lancie, left, Marnie Mosiman 
and Don Sparks in "Man and Superman." DON KELSEN / Los Angeles Times; Photo, 
(Orange County Edition) Mosiman and De Lancie in a "Man and Superman" that has 
its shining moments but is not up to the usual Shavian standard at South Coast 
Repertory. ROD BOREN / For The Times 
</P>
