Palestinians gather at Mile Square Regional Park. ; Photo, Misty Jones, 13, 
bearing flag, points the way for members of a support group of military 
families meeting in Anaheim. The group was the idea of Kathy Collier of Buena 
Park whose son Darrin went to Saudi Arabia in August. ; Photo, At meeting 
Jackie Brewer, 21, holds 3-week-old daughter, Latisha, born seven hours after 
her Marine father left for Saudi Arabia. GAIL FISHER / Los Angeles Times 
