REAGANS TAKE OFF FOR EUROPE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Wire Services 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Former President Ronald Reagan left Los Angeles by plane today for Berlin on 
his way to meet European leaders and address the Soviet Parliament. 
</P>
<P>
