<P>
Sheriff's deputies acting on an anonymous tip broke up a party involving about 
200 men and up to 20 women performing a variety of sexual acts, authorities 
said today. 
</P>
<P>
Four women ranging from 21 to 25 years old were arrested for investigation of 
lewd conduct in a public place after the 6 p.m. Sunday raid at a banquet hall 
near Los Angeles International Airport, Sheriff's Deputy Gabe Ramirez said. 
</P>
<P>
Deputies said they saw between 16 and 20 nude women engaging in a number of 
sexual acts with the men on the floor and on various tables. 
</P>
<P>
About 30 men were detained for questioning, Ramirez said. 
