Photo, Hello Again, Norma Jean: A photographer on assignment for Redbook 
magazine caught Marilyn Monroe in a last-minute touch-up before attending the 
1955 Broadway premier of "Cat on a Hot Tin Roof." Never published, the picture 
languished in a warehouse before an archivist bought it and various others 
sight-unseen in 1987. Redbook 
